    title: "Frame Check Methodology"
    authors:
      - family-names: Lucic
        given-names: Lovro
    url: "https://github.com/lluvr/frame-check-mcp/blob/master/METHODOLOGY.md"
    license: CC-BY-4.0
    year: 2026
    notes: "Bundled with the frame-check-mcp PyPI wheel as METHODOLOGY.md. The hosted corpus surface at https://frame.clarethium.com/corpus/methodology/ is paused while production is paused; the canonical text is the bundled file."
